query:
SELECT
            tm.id::text as "id!",
            tm.email as "user_email",
            tm.role as "to_role",
            tm.joined_at as "timestamp!"
           FROM team_members tm
           JOIN teams t ON tm.team_id = t.id
           WHERE t.tenant_workspace_id = $1
           ORDER BY tm.joined_at DESC
           LIMIT 10
